WEBVTT

00:02.160 --> 00:04.117
[♪♪♪]

00:04.520 --> 00:07.433
ANNOUNCER:
<i>This is the story of two sisters:</i>

00:07.640 --> 00:11.395
<i>Jessica Tate and Mary Campbell.</i>

00:11.600 --> 00:15.958
<i>Jessica lives in a neighbourhood</i>
<i>known as rich.</i>

00:16.160 --> 00:17.753
<i>Jessica likes life.</i>

00:17.960 --> 00:20.794
<i>The only thing about life</i>
<i>she would change, if she could,</i>

00:21.000 --> 00:23.560
<i>is that she would set it</i>
<i>all to music.</i>

00:24.880 --> 00:28.396
<i>The Tates have more secrets</i>
<i>than they do money.</i>

00:31.200 --> 00:34.352
<i>We're approaching</i>
<i>Mary Campbell's house.</i>

00:36.160 --> 00:37.753
<i>Mary, too, likes life.</i>

00:37.960 --> 00:41.795
<i>Unfortunately, life doesn't seem</i>
<i>to be too crazy about her.</i>

00:42.000 --> 00:45.391
<i>As you can see, the Campbells</i>
<i>don't have nearly as much money</i>

00:45.600 --> 00:46.750
<i>as the Tates.</i>

00:47.480 --> 00:51.235
<i>They do, however,</i>
<i>have as many secrets.</i>

00:54.920 --> 00:55.920
[♪♪♪]

00:56.080 --> 00:57.201
<i>In the last episode of</i> Soap,

00:57.240 --> 00:59.630
<i>Chief Tinkler informed the Tates</i>
<i>and the Campbells</i>

00:59.840 --> 01:01.911
<i>that they are all suspects</i>
<i>in the murder</i>

01:02.120 --> 01:04.032
<i>of Peter Campbell, the tennis pro,</i>

01:04.239 --> 01:08.314
<i>because all of them had a motive</i>
<i>and most of them don't have an alibi.</i>

01:08.520 --> 01:11.080
<i>Chester, who knew Jessica</i>
<i>had had an affair,</i>

01:11.280 --> 01:13.431
<i>but didn't know who</i>
<i>she had her affair with,</i>

01:13.640 --> 01:15.597
<i>found out her affair</i>
<i>had been with Peter.</i>

01:16.120 --> 01:17.759
<i>Of course, before his death.</i>

01:17.960 --> 01:23.194
<i>Confused? You won't be</i>
<i>after this week's episode of</i> Soap.

01:24.080 --> 01:26.151
<i>We begin this week's episode</i>
<i>of</i> Soap

01:26.360 --> 01:30.593
<i>shortly after Chief Tinkler</i>
<i>has left the stunned families.</i>

01:32.000 --> 01:38.074
